WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:30.682 --> 00:00:32.082
Did you--

00:00:42.594 --> 00:00:44.228
Have you ever
had a dream, neo,

00:00:44.296 --> 00:00:46.230
That you were
so sure was real?

00:00:46.298 --> 00:00:48.232
[thunder]

00:00:48.300 --> 00:00:50.734
What if you were unable
to wake from that dream?

00:00:50.802 --> 00:00:52.736
How would you
know the difference

00:00:52.804 --> 00:00:54.238
Between the dream world

00:00:54.306 --> 00:00:56.240
And the real world?

00:00:56.308 --> 00:00:58.742
This can't be.

00:00:58.810 --> 00:01:00.244
Be what?

